data.description: This stunning ranch home sits on a spacious and picturesque 2 1/2-acre lot. The front of the house is adorned with large windows, allowing ample natural light to filter through. Garage and Work Garage: To the side of the house, there is a overside garage with an automatic door opener. The garage provides convenient parking space and storage for vehicles. Adjacent to the garage is a separate work garage, designed for those who enjoy working on projects, whether it be woodworking, automotive repairs, or any other hobbies requiring a dedicated workspace. Upon entering the ranch home through the front door, you step into a welcoming foyer. The main living areas, including the living room, dining room, and kitchen, feature an open floor plan, creating a spacious and airy atmosphere. Large windows throughout the house allow for abundant natural light, while also providing scenic views. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, ample countertop space. The adjacent dining area offers plenty of room for family meals and entertaining guests. The living room is open with plenty of room for comfortable seating, is a perfect place to relax and unwind. This ranch home includes three well-appointed bedrooms, each with its own closet space.The 2 1/2 acres of land offer plenty of room for outdoor activities and enjoyment. The backyard features a nice sized deck, perfect for hosting barbecues or simply lounging in the fresh air. Additionally, there is an outside storage unit, providing extra space for storing gardening tools, outdoor furniture, or any other items you may need. Overall, this ranch-style home offers a comfortable and spacious living environment, combining modern design with functional features. It provides a tranquil retreat on 2 1/2 acres of land, complete with a garage, outside storage unit, and a work garage for those who enjoy hands-on projects. It is a must see !!!!!!  --   Brianna Tennant
